snippet.title: 5 Controversies That Warner Bros Scored in 2020 | Flixet
snippet.description:
In today’s video are going to tell about 5 Controversies That Warner Bros Scored in 2020. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
______________________________________________________

It is not a great year to be in Warner Bros' legal team. You can imagine the hours they must have been putting in dealing with crisis after crisis. The world-renowned studio has stirred quite a few controversies in 2020 that shook everyone. Accusations have been made. Lawsuits might be in the pipeline. A prominent actor has been fired. And worse of all, the studio might also face the wrath of the cancel gang! We are rounding up some of the controversial, headline-grabbing stuff that went down at Warner's this year.
